        "liquid": "<div class=\"info-meta-page\">\n  <h1>Linen and Co - Lead Times and Manufacturing</h1>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Manufacturing Approach</h2>\n    <h3>Made-to-Order Production Excellence</h3>\n    <p>Linen and Co operates on a sophisticated made-to-order manufacturing model, ensuring that every piece of linen is crafted with precision, quality, and customisation specifically for each valued client. This approach guarantees freshness, eliminates waste, and allows for personalised specifications that meet the exact needs of our discerning customers.</p>\n    <p>Our artisanal approach means that each product begins its journey only after your order is confirmed, ensuring optimal quality control and the ability to accommodate special requests, custom sizing, and personalised branding requirements.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Made-to-Order Products Include</h2>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Fitted sheets – Custom-sized for perfect mattress fit</li>\n      <li>Flat sheets – Luxuriously crafted for ultimate comfort</li>\n      <li>Duvet covers – Available in various sizes and custom designs</li>\n      <li>Pillowcases – Standard, king, and custom sizes available</li>\n      <li>Mattress protectors – Waterproof and breathable options</li>\n      <li>Pillow protectors – Hypoallergenic and dust-mite resistant</li>\n      <li>Mattress convertors and toppers – Enhanced comfort solutions</li>\n      <li>Scatter pillows – Decorative and functional accent pieces</li>\n      <li>Bed end runners – Elegant finishing touches</li>\n      <li>Table linen – Custom tablecloths, runners, and napkins</li>\n      <li>Duvet inners and pillows – Premium filling materials</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Delivery Timelines</h2>\n    <h3>Made-to-Order Items: 3–14 Working Days</h3>\n    <p>Timeline calculated from payment clearance and varies based on:</p>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Order size and complexity</li>\n      <li>Current production schedule</li>\n      <li>Product specifications</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Ready-Made Items: 2–4 Days</h3>\n    <p>Quick dispatch for standard inventory items:</p>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Base covers</li>\n      <li>Blankets</li>\n      <li>Towels</li>\n      <li>Gowns</li>\n      <li>Slippers</li>\n      <li>Quilted bedspreads</li>\n      <li>Ready-made curtains</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Stock Availability</h2>\n    <h3>Ready-Made Item Considerations</h3>\n    <p>We strive to maintain optimal stock levels. In cases where specific designs or qualities are unavailable:</p>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Substitutions may be necessary</li>\n      <li>Customers will be promptly notified</li>\n      <li>Alternative options will be proposed</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Satin Stitch Embroidery Processing</h2>\n    <h3>Single Row Satin Stitch</h3>\n    <p>+1 Week</p>\n    <h3>Double Row Satin Stitch</h3>\n    <p>+2 Weeks</p>\n    <p>Embroidery requires meticulous craftsmanship. Customers should note:</p>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Intricate designs need additional time</li>\n      <li>No liability for laundering damage</li>\n      <li>Follow care instructions carefully</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Contact Information</h2>\n    <ul class=\"info-list\">\n      <li>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@linenco.co.za\">info@linenco.co.za</a></li>\n      <li>Phone: <a href=\"tel:0101094950\">010 109 4950</a></li>\n      <li>WhatsApp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/27662918292\">066 291 8292</a></li>\n      <li>Address: 5 1st Avenue, Edenvale, Gauteng, 1609, South Africa</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"info-block\">\n    <h2 class=\"section-heading\">Customer Acknowledgement</h2>\n    <p>By utilising Linen and Co’s services, customers explicitly acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined in this Lead Times Policy. This includes understanding our manufacturing processes, delivery timelines, and potential factors that may influence production and shipping.</p>\n    <p>We appreciate your trust and commitment to quality. Our team is dedicated to providing exceptional service and maintaining the highest standards of craftsmanship.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"disclaimer-link\">\n    <a href=\"/policies/terms-of-service\" class=\"secondary-button\">Review Terms of Service →</a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.linenco.co.za/pages/contact\" class=\"secondary-button\">Contact Us →</a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"effective-date\">\n    <p>Effective Date: 19 January 2026</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.info-meta-page {\n  max-width: 800px;\n  margin: 40px auto;\n  padding: 20px;\n  background: #fff;\n  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;\n  color: #333;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n.info-meta-page h1 {\n  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;\n  font-size: 2em;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: 28px;\n  color: #333;\n  letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n}\n.info-meta-page .info-block {\n  background: #f8f8f8;\n  border: 1px solid #d1d1d1;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  padding: 20px 18px 16px 18px;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n.info-meta-page .section-heading {\n  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  font-size: 1.08rem;\n  letter-spacing: 0.09em;\n  margin: 0 0 14px 0;\n  color: #333;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n  padding-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.info-meta-page h3 {\n  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  font-size: 1em;\n  letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n  margin: 14px 0 6px 0;\n  color: #333;\n}\n.info-meta-page p,\n.info-meta-page li {\n  font-family: 'Nunito'